General Information

Lather & shave in one easy step! No Shave gel required

The Schick Intuition Sensitive Care skin conditioning solid contains 100% natural Aloe and Vitamin E. It's hypoallergenic, gentle on your skin, moisturises dry skin during shaving, and will leave skin feeling smooth. It also features a 4-blade pivoting head to glide smoothly along the contours of your legs and body.
